<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267867>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1 – 6. 1. Rhaphium apophysatum sp. nov.; 2. R. bilobum sp. nov.; 3. R. bisectum sp. nov.; 4. R. daqinggouense sp. nov.; 5. R. dorsiseta sp. nov.; 6. R. neimengense sp. nov. All male. Scale bar = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267867/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267869>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 12. Rhaphium bisectum sp. nov., male. 11. Antenna, scale bar = 0.2 mm; 12. Male genitalia, lateral view, scale bar = 0.2 mm. Abbreviations: hyp = hypandrium, epl = epandrial lobe, sur = surstylus, cer = cercus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267869/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267870>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 17. Rhaphium dorsiseta sp. nov., male. 15. Antenna, scale bar = 0.2 mm; 16. Male genitalia, lateral view, scale bar = 0.2 mm. 17. Male fore tarsomere 5. v Abbreviations: hyp = hypandrium, epl = epandrial lobe, ph = phallus, sur = surstylus, cer = cercus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267870/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267868>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 8. Rhaphium apophysatum sp. nov., male. 7. Antenna, scale bar = 0.2 mm; 8. Male genitalia, lateral view, scale bar = 0.2 mm. Abbreviations: hyp = hypandrium, ph = phallus, sur = surstylus, cer = cercus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267868/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

